name: 玛雅·曼科
introduction: Maya Manko was born in Southern California. Inspired by her older sister, she began her acting journey in musical theater at the age of seven. Since then, she has appeared in numerous films and commercials.Maya's talents extend beyond acting. She is also a dedicated gymnast and cheerleader, known for her remarkable skills and unwavering determination.In her free time, Maya enjoys performing gravity-defying gymnastic tricks and showering her pets with love and care.
